Before You Start Using the OmniStudio Build Tool

Before you start, understand the available and recommended authentication methods, the command syntax, and how the job file works.

Authentication Methods for the OmniStudio Build Tool
Use one of three available authentication methods: Salesforce DX CLI, org properties files, or OAuth authentication. Salesforce DX CLI is recommended.
Export and Deployment Tools
Use the correct command syntax and specify the proper data pack type. Use a job file to define the export and deploy process settings.
